# CODEOWNERS - Documentation and MCP Governance
#
# This file defines ownership patterns for the marketing-websites monorepo
# following 2026 enterprise governance standards with clear responsibility assignment.
#
# Format: <pattern> <owner1> <owner2> <...>
# - pattern: file path pattern (supports wildcards)
# - owners: GitHub usernames, team names (@team-name), or email addresses
#
# Priority: Top-to-bottom. First matching pattern wins.
#
# Documentation: docs/CODEOWNERS.md
# ADR: docs/architecture/decisions/ADR-001-codeowners-governance.md

# ==============================================================================
# GLOBAL OWNERSHIP - Executive Oversight
# ==============================================================================

# Root repository - Executive team
* @trevorlam @executive-team

# Critical security files - Security team
SECURITY.md @security-team @trevorlam
**/SECURITY.md @security-team
**/.github/SECURITY.md @security-team

# Enterprise governance - Architecture board
ARCHITECTURE_PLAN.md @architecture-board @trevorlam
GOVERNANCE.md @architecture-board
